@startuml
title CRUD - Update
actor Client
participant Controller
participant Service
participant Repository

Client -> Controller : PUT /resources/{id}\nUpdateResourceRequest
Controller -> Service : update(id, request)
Service -> Repository : findById(id)
Repository --> Service : existingEntity
alt exists
  Service -> Repository : save(updatedEntity)
  Repository --> Service : updatedEntity
  Service --> Controller : ResourceResponse
  Controller --> Client : 200 OK
else not exists
  Controller --> Client : 404 Not Found
end

note right of Service
- Validate changes
- Enforce business constraints
- Transactional
end note
@enduml